secs. 23 to 26, inclusive;
sec. 27, E½;
sec. 34, E½;
secs. 35 and 36.
This refuge shall be known as the Sand Lake Migratory Waterfowl Refuge.
FRANKLIN D. ROOSEVELT
The White House,
September 4, 1935.
